jparsec.ephem.planets.imcce

Class Elp2000_data2

  • java.lang.Object
    • jparsec.ephem.planets.imcce.Elp2000_data2

  • public class Elp2000_data2
extends java.lang.Object
    All the static data of the ELP2000 theory (part 2), in a separate file for managability. The whole theory is applied. This is part 2 (from 2) of the data.

    Library users can ignore this class.

    Reference

    ELP 2000-85: a semi-analytical lunar ephemeris adequate for historical times. Chapront-Touze M., Chapront J. Astron. and Astrophys. 190, 342 (1988).

    Since:
    version 1.0
    Author:
    T. Alonso Albi - OAN (Spain)
